        <mxCell id="J5HSsrHVb95wKQD47Bpc-20" value="Variables :&lt;br&gt;isConfigMode - bool,true if config mode is on&lt;br&gt;isBoosted - bool, true if action Blizzard event SHOW_ACTIVATION_OVERLAY_GLOW_SHOW&lt;br&gt;isUsable - bool,true if action can be used&lt;br&gt;notEnoughMana - bool, true if user dont have enoug mana&lt;br&gt;duration - number, value of current active cooldown&lt;br&gt;isResting - bool, true if user is in rest zone&lt;br&gt;globalHideRest- bool, true if user check to action be hidden in rest zone&lt;br&gt;displayOnlyWhenBoosted - true, if user select that action should be displayed only when boosted&lt;br&gt;inRange - bool, true if user is in range for spell&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;isUserBuffedBy - bool, true if user is buffed with same spell&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;isPVPing = bool,true if user have Warmode on&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;isPVPspell = bool, true is spell is pvp talent&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" parent="1" vertex="1">
